battlePhrases: {"Start": "Hmmm. MegaBit activity in this area seems to be strong. I wonder why.","Loss": "That was an excellent battle. How long have you had those MegaBits?","Win": "Scientifically speaking, it would appear that I have beaten you."}
name: Scientist

battlePhrases: {"Start": "I LOVE pixels! That's why I like MegaBits so much.","Loss": "That battle gave me an idea for a website design...","Win": "I beat you before it was cool."}
name: Hipster
tradePhrases: {"Start":"I have almost as many MegaBits as I have scarves!","Accept":"It's no scarf, but I'll trade!","Reject":"I won't even take that trade ironically."}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "I've read three different books on MegaBits and I think I'm ready to battle!","Loss": "Better hit the books!","Win": "Boy, I really schooled you!"}
name: Student
tradePhrases: {"Start":"We talked about barter in my cultural anthropology class.","Accept":"That trade is Dean's List quality!","Reject":"You flunked out of this trade."}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "::huff huff huff:: A battle? Sure! I can use a break.","Loss": "I guess we have more training to do! ::huff huff huff huff huff::","Win": "Talk about keeping my heart rate up!"}
name: Jogger

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Whatcha gonna do when my MegaBits come for you?","Loss": "You have the right to remain silent about that battle.","Win": "One step closer to my quota!"}
name: Officer

battlePhrases: {"Start": "I battle fire, how hard can it be to battle a few MegaBits?","Loss": "Well, now I just feel put out.","Win": "Now I'M on fire!"}
name: Firefighter

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Yo, we gonna battle or what?","Loss": "That was just luck, man.","Win": "Aw yeah, MegaBits!"}
name: Vagrant
tradePhrases: {"Start":"Yo, you holding? Let's trade.","Accept":"Sick trade!","Reject":"Uh, no way, man."}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Mummy and Daddy said my MegaBits will keep me safe!","Loss": "Nooooo!","Win": "Nanny-nanny-boo-boo!"}
name: Little Kid

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Huh? Fight? I guess.","Loss": "Everything's meaningless anyway.","Win": "Whatever."}
name: Goth Kid
tradePhrases: {"Start":"I guess we can trade. Whatever.","Accept":"Possessions are meaningless in this black void. Except the ones you just gave me.","Reject":"Instead of that, I'll trade you my nothing for your nothing."}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "MegaBits are exciting, but so are plants. I'm torn!","Loss": "Maybe I should stick to plants and leaf MegaBits alone.","Win": "Consider yourself weed-whacked!"}
name: Gardener

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Back in home country, we fight bear long before MegaBits.","Loss": "(Quiet sobbing)","Win": "You must grin and bear it."}
name: Bear Wrestler

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Can you believe it's only been a year since MegaBits were discovered?","Loss": "How did you and your MegaBits get so strong so fast?","Win": "I beat you like no one ever has!"}
name: New Trainer
tradePhrases: {"Start":"Can you believe it's only been a year since MegaBits were discovered?","Accept":"That trade is the very best!","Reject":"No dice!"}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "What's all this buzz about MegaBit battles, anyway?","Loss": "You smoked me!","Win": "That's gotta sting."}
name: Bee-Keeper
tradePhrases: {"Start":"Trading is like the symbiotic relationship between a bee and a flower.","Accept":"Oh honey, that's a sweet trade.","Reject":"Buzz off!"}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "A MegaBits trainer walks into a barâ€¦","Loss": "Ouch, denied!","Win": "Welcome to Club Loser, population: YOU."}
name: Bouncer

battlePhrases: {"Start": "OH. EM. GEE. Look how CUTE your megabits are!","Loss": "That was, like, SO. Not. Cute.","Win": "Weee!"}
name: Cute Fanatic

battlePhrases: {"Start": "I'm raising my MegaBits on a raw diet, just like me!","Loss": "Maybe they do need more protein.","Win": "You're a medi-okra trainer at best."}
name: Vegan

battlePhrases: {"Start": "How many MegaBits do YOU have?","Loss": "I think I just need more MegaBits.","Win": "Just another victory to add to my collection."}
name: Collector

battlePhrases: {"Start": "I love starting things.","Loss": "Ouch,  down in flames.","Win": "You got some ice for that burn?"}
name: Pyro

battlePhrases: {"Start": "If you hold a shell to your ear, you can hear me about to beat you in battle!","Loss": "That was gnarly.","Win": "You can't catch every wave, dude."}
name: Surfer
tradePhrases: {"Start":"Trading would be tubular, bro!","Accept":"Gnarly! I, like, accept your trade.","Reject":"That trade would be totally bogus, dude!"}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "You want a peace of me?","Loss": "You're really harshing my mellow.","Win": "Groovy!"}
name: Hippy
tradePhrases: {"Start":"You wanna trade, man? ","Accept":"Sure thing, dude!","Reject":"Love should be free but my possessions aren't. No trade."}

battlePhrases: {"Start": "Pardon me, but I do believe I've dropped my gauntlet.","Loss": "Oh, dear!","Win": "What a pleasure this has been."}
name: Lady

battlePhrases: {"Start": "You wanna battle against me, do ya?","Loss": "Up yours! ","Win": "Take that, the man!"}
name: Punk

battlePhrases: {"Start": "You remind me of this one shaman I met in Mali.","Loss": "I didn't come halfway around the world for this!","Win": "You know, in some cultures, the loser of a battle is considered the winner."}
name: Traveler
tradePhrases: {"Start":"In some cultures, barter is still the primary form of economy.","Accept":"That will be useful on my next trip!","Reject":"Why in the world would I accept that trade?"}
